                  WHEN COALESCE(uo.new_topic_duration_minutes, 2880) = -1 THEN u.created_at
                  WHEN COALESCE(uo.new_topic_duration_minutes, 2880) = -2 THEN COALESCE(u.previous_visit_at,u.created_at)

       COALESCE(ft.title, ftl.title) AS title,
       ftl.link_topic_id,
       ftl.reflection,
       ftl.internal,
       ftl.domain,
       MIN(ftl.user_id) AS user_id,
       SUM(clicks) AS clicks
FROM topic_links AS ftl
LEFT JOIN topics AS ft ON ftl.link_topic_id = ft.id
LEFT JOIN categories AS c ON c.id = ft.category_id
WHERE (ftl.topic_id = 7) AND (ft.deleted_at IS NULL) AND (NOT(ftl.url ILIKE '%.png' OR ftl.url ILIKE '%.jpg' OR ftl.url ILIKE '%.gif')) AND (COALESCE(ft.archetype, 'regular') <> 'private_message') AND (clicks > 0) AND (NOT COALESCE(c.read_restricted, false) OR c.id in (3,4))
GROUP BY ftl.url, ft.title, ftl.title, ftl.link_topic_id, ftl.reflection, ftl.internal, ftl.domain
ORDER BY clicks DESC, count(*) DESC
LIMIT 50
